title: Blissful Belly Vegetarian Cuisine
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Fast food, Take-out, Bakery, Fusion, Filipino
description: Restaurant and shop. Some raw foods, raw cakes, and other vegan options for breads and pastries made from organic flour. No eggs used, only "gardenia" brean has milk. Also some hot foods. Formerly named Satya's.
streetAddress: 77 Xavierville Ave, 2nd Floor, Llannar Bldg, Quezon City
